item.title: Help?
item.dc:creator: @bryanc Bryanc
item.description:
@bryanc wrote:

Yeah, close fire-fox if thats what you’re using.

When you close the browser then, right click the icon for the browser and run it as a administrator. That gives it administrative powers to be able to read/write data on the hard drive. Thus, allowing the cache to download. Hope it helps.
